@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gxwbgy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.18 + tmp + 0.75) * v1) - v0)
    tmp = 0.99
    tmp = (0.64 * wp.cos(0.97))
    v1 = v2
    v0 = (tmp - v1)
    data[tid] = v0
